120
00:09:17,230 --> 00:09:19,920
Yes, Hua Family has no other way out.

121
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:23,040
Hua Que is probably looking for Hua Xiaolei now.

122
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:24,980
What Hua Xiaolei?

123
00:09:24,980 --> 00:09:27,780
She is now Little Chun Hua.

124
00:09:27,780 --> 00:09:32,060
Since she has lost her memory, I will not treat her the same way that I treated Hua Xiaolei.

125
00:09:32,060 --> 00:09:36,610
Miss Chun Hua and Hua Xiaolei are indeed like two different people.

126
