136
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:17,350
- Their ability has already fallen short of their wishes. 
 - It couldn't be better.

137
00:10:20,100 --> 00:10:24,550
Eating mooncakes and acting as her family are merely an adjustment.

138
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:27,590
It's so relaxed and cheerful, it's not a burden,

139
00:10:27,590 --> 00:10:30,520
