140
00:10:31,570 --> 00:10:34,540
So, Ye Xingzhu, what are you worried about?

141
00:10:35,300 --> 00:10:37,190
You even intentionally mentioned Fulou.

142
00:10:37,190 --> 00:10:39,120
Everything is under your control.

143
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:42,600
- I shouldn't have doubted it. 
 - I don't blame you.

144
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,740
Go and see how Hua Que is doing.

145
00:10:44,740 --> 00:10:46,450
Yes.

146
