157
00:12:06,190 --> 00:12:09,100
- Miss Chun Hua. 
 - Xiao Bai?

158
00:12:18,010 --> 00:12:22,680
That to say, I'm Xiao Bai's destiny!

159
00:12:30,650 --> 00:12:32,800
Not right!

160
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:38,460
- What are you doing? 
 - Weren't you suspicious that I am lying to you?

161
00:12:38,460 --> 00:12:40,760
On your body, you have a pink birthmark.

162
00:12:40,760 --> 00:12:44,100
It's in the shape of a flower bud. That's the reason why you were named Chun Hua.

163
00:12:44,100 --> 00:12:46,180
My brother said it was a birthmark.

164
00:12:46,180 --> 00:12:48,620
Xiao Bai said it was a scar.

165
00:12:48,620 --> 00:12:51,340
Did he lie to me?

166
00:12:52,990 --> 00:12:56,990
- Who is it? 
 - Open the door. It's older brother.

167
00:12:59,500 --> 00:13:03,770
You shouldn't imitate other people's voices, I simply don't know if it's you.

168
00:13:03,770 --> 00:13:08,590
Besides, isn't it easy for you to enter wherever you want? Do you still need me to open the door for you?

169
00:13:08,590 --> 00:13:10,950
Xiaolei, quickly open the door!

170
00:13:11,650 --> 00:13:15,970
Xiaolei? How can older brother know I'm called Xiaolei.

171
00:13:28,040 --> 00:13:29,980
You are really belong to Hua family!

172
00:13:29,980 --> 00:13:32,440
I'm your older brother!

173
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:35,700
Have you lost your memory? Can't you remember me?

174
00:13:38,490 --> 00:13:40,350
Let's talk inside!

175
00:13:47,780 --> 00:13:49,720
What are you talking about?

176
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:53,840
Right now, we only have one option, leave as far away as you can from the Hua family.

177
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:56,090
The further, the better! Never come back again.

178
00:13:56,090 --> 00:13:58,410
From now on, you are not Hua Xiaolei.

179
00:13:58,410 --> 00:14:00,940
I'm also not your older brother; even more so, you aren't their daughter.

180
00:14:00,940 --> 00:14:04,230
The matter between you and Shangguan Qiu Yue has brought shame upon the entire Hua family.

181
00:14:04,230 --> 00:14:06,320
Wait...

182
00:14:07,130 --> 00:14:10,700
What happened between Shangguan Qiu Yue and I?

183
00:14:10,700 --> 00:14:12,880
You don't remember?

184
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:23,940
You mean I even...

185
00:14:27,190 --> 00:14:31,570
I... Shangguan Qiu Yue and I...

186
00:14:31,570 --> 00:14:33,830
had a love affair?

187
00:14:39,020 --> 00:14:42,660
- This is impossible. 
 - If it weren't for this matter, why would I come to see you now?

188
00:14:42,660 --> 00:14:46,820
In Shangguan Qiu Yue's eyes, I'm just a joke.

189
00:14:46,820 --> 00:14:51,490
He called me 'little sister' so many times, but it has actually all been a lie.

190
00:14:51,490 --> 00:14:54,900
This matter, you promised not to judge.

191
00:14:58,110 --> 00:15:01,100
Does Xiao Bai know?

192
00:15:01,100 --> 00:15:03,950
If he knows, it won't be just you,

193
00:15:03,950 --> 00:15:05,570
but the entire Hua family will suffer.

194
00:15:05,570 --> 00:15:09,570
Take advantage of the fact that Xiao Bai still hasn't discovered this yet, it would be best if you never returned again.

195
00:15:12,180 --> 00:15:15,650
Xiao Bai said he would take me to Hua's family tomorrow.

196
00:15:15,650 --> 00:15:18,080
I don't care about all that, figure it out yourself!

197
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,700
- But... 
 - No but.

198
00:15:19,700 --> 00:15:22,470
But what does this have to do with me?

199
00:15:24,090 --> 00:15:26,480
I mean to say.

200
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:28,840
That was the past.

201
00:15:28,840 --> 00:15:30,760
I'm not Hua Xiaolei. I'm Chun Hua.

202
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:33,640
If that's the case, don't blame me if I don't think of the love between a brother and a sister.

203
00:15:33,640 --> 00:15:37,570
Tomorrow, when we see each other, father and I absolutely will not acknowledge you.

204
00:16:02,820 --> 00:16:07,130
Sister, haven't you died once?

205
00:16:08,330 --> 00:16:11,340
Now, if you can just disappear completely,

206
00:16:12,490 --> 00:16:14,890
only then, can I protect the Hua family.

207
00:16:43,640 --> 00:16:45,170
You killed him?

208
00:16:45,170 --> 00:16:48,880
- He wanted to set a fire and kill Hua— 
 - I'm not asking about him, I'm asking you.

209
00:16:48,880 --> 00:16:51,460
Who told you to kill Hua Que?

210
00:16:52,650 --> 00:16:54,680
It's all my fault.

211
00:16:56,210 --> 00:16:59,310
Little Chun Hua has no brother now, can you compensate her for her loss?

212
00:16:59,310 --> 00:17:00,870
I...

213
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:14,300
Have no brother...

214
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:20,890
Then I'm the only one who can compensate her with a brother, for you.

215
00:17:20,890 --> 00:17:23,540
- Master. 
 - Stand up.

216
00:17:24,960 --> 00:17:27,130
Little Chun Hua doesn't want to be my sister

217
00:17:27,130 --> 00:17:29,060
but I still partially want to be her brother.

218
00:17:29,060 --> 00:17:30,850
Master.

219
00:17:34,280 --> 00:17:38,150
I've disrupted every corner of the world and now, I've gotten the opportunity to have a sister.

220
00:17:38,150 --> 00:17:41,440
It's truly killing two birds with one stone, I'm pleased.

221
00:17:47,270 --> 00:17:52,080
Furthermore, in the future, do not mention Fulou.

222
00:17:52,080 --> 00:17:54,170
I am not Fulou.

223
00:17:54,170 --> 00:17:57,140
I won't indulge myself in a love affair.

224
00:17:57,140 --> 00:17:58,850
Yes.

225
00:18:14,830 --> 00:18:19,980
I received an order from your son to come and support the Hua family in resolving this little annoyance of Xiao Bai.

226
00:18:19,980 --> 00:18:23,840
