Right now, I'm afraid they won't recognize each other.

240
00:19:23,080 --> 00:19:27,420
If it's so, that's good also!

241
00:19:29,280 --> 00:19:34,600
 [Yingzhen Inn] 

242
00:19:40,780 --> 00:19:44,450
Miss Chun Hua, it's time to go.

243
00:19:48,130 --> 00:19:49,810
Wait a moment!

244
00:20:03,100 --> 00:20:05,180
Miss Chun Hua.

245
00:20:08,020 --> 00:20:09,960
Miss Chun Hua.

246
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:15,180
I'm going in, okay?

247
00:20:16,900 --> 00:20:18,980
Miss Chun Hua.

248
00:20:27,820 --> 00:20:29,800
Chun Hua.

249
00:20:42,980 --> 00:20:44,890
Xiao Bai?

250
00:20:44,890 --> 00:20:47,400
- Miss Chun Hua? 
 - I don't know.

251
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:49,670
I clearly just heard her when knocking.

252
00:20:49,670 --> 00:20:52,580
Today, clearly she doesn't know how to face it.

253
00:20:52,580 --> 00:20:54,880
So she hides alone.

254
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:58,290
Heaven protects me through this.

255
00:21:01,220 --> 00:21:05,880
In that case, let's wait for Miss Chun Hua to figure it out.

256
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:09,920
Until that moment comes, just give her time to make a decision.

257
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:12,860
No, absolutely not! This matter cannot be delayed.

258
00:21:12,860 --> 00:21:16,820
Brother Xiao, no way!

259
00:21:16,820 --> 00:21:19,290
- Go, go, go on! 
 - This...

260
00:21:37,350 --> 00:21:39,830
Finally gone!

261
00:22:05,820 --> 00:22:07,780
Miss Chun Hua.

262
00:22:14,340 --> 00:22:19,430
 [Hua Residence] 

263
00:22:23,490 --> 00:22:25,670
If it comes to it, I'll just keep pretending that I lost my memory.

264
00:22:25,670 --> 00:22:27,840
This won't hinder me.

265
00:22:43,470 --> 00:22:47,200
I'm done for! They're fighting again.

266
00:22:50,370 --> 00:22:53,970
Younger Sister, where were you?

267
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:56,990
You...

268
00:22:57,940 --> 00:23:00,060
Did you freeze or starve?

269
00:23:01,380 --> 00:23:05,010
That can't be! Even Xiao Bai has never seen Shangguan Qiu Yue?

270
00:23:05,010 --> 00:23:07,210
Did someone bully you?

271
00:23:09,310 --> 00:23:11,460
Could it be that you lost your memory?

272
00:23:13,710 --> 00:23:16,550
What made my Little Sister to become so injured like this?

273
00:23:19,520 --> 00:23:24,100
So it's Brother Hua. Excuse me! I beg you pardon.

274
00:23:24,100 --> 00:23:27,910
 Xiao Bai hasn't seen Hua Que before, either, has he?

275
00:23:30,700 --> 00:23:33,730
Yesterday, my father offended you.

276
00:23:33,730 --> 00:23:35,990
I hope Hero Xiao will understand.

277
00:23:35,990 --> 00:23:39,960
Not at all! I was too impulsive and, thus, have offended Old Master Hua.

278
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:42,390
Older Brother Hua, please don't take it to heart.

279
00:23:42,390 --> 00:23:44,930
We're one family. Let's not talk like strangers.

280
00:23:44,930 --> 00:23:46,760
Please enter!

281
00:23:46,760 --> 00:23:48,490
Pardon me.

282
00:23:54,230 --> 00:23:59,300
Hero Xiao, my father is holding this feast as an apology.

283
00:23:59,300 --> 00:24:01,650
I hope Hero Xiao will appreciate it.

284
00:24:01,650 --> 00:24:04,450
- Many thanks to Master Hua. 
 - Please!

285
00:24:10,190 --> 00:24:12,770
What happened yesterday is so offensive.

286
00:24:12,770 --> 00:24:15,400
I hope that Nephew (endearing term to call a son of a friend) will be generous to overlook it.

287
00:24:15,400 --> 00:24:18,680
Little girl has returned safely now.

288
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:21,630
It is all thanks to you.

289
00:24:21,630 --> 00:24:24,580
This old man will toast you once.

290
00:24:35,030 --> 00:24:39,860
It was my negligence. I should have investigated clearly before coming.

291
00:24:42,230 --> 00:24:43,960
Little Sister.

292
00:24:56,770 --> 00:24:59,180
Brother Hua, why did you sigh?

293
00:24:59,730 --> 00:25:02,500
Hero Xiao, you might not know,

294
00:25:03,110 --> 00:25:07,280
My little sister and I have been inseparable since childhood while growing up.

295
00:25:07,280 --> 00:25:09,390
Whatever it is, as long as she likes it,

296
00:25:09,390 --> 00:25:12,560
even if it was the moon in the sky,

297
00:25:12,560 --> 00:25:16,100
I wouldn't hesitate any bit to take it off and give it to her.

298
00:25:16,100 --> 00:25:18,260
What a pity!

299
00:25:21,510 --> 00:25:26,350
When I found out my little sister had died in the fire,

300
00:25:26,350 --> 00:25:31,230
I couldn't stop my tears from streaming down my face, nor could I eat or drink.

301
00:25:34,170 --> 00:25:36,570
Now,

302
00:25:36,570 --> 00:25:41,320
it's even so hard for Little Sister to call me Older Brother.

303
00:25:45,380 --> 00:25:47,460
Forget it!

304
00:25:47,990 --> 00:25:50,420
It's all because Older Brother is not good

305
00:25:51,560 --> 00:25:54,950
to let you suffer through so much.

306
00:25:54,950 --> 00:25:58,330
When will you stop acting this scene?

307
00:26:01,370 --> 00:26:03,180
Xiaolei,

308
00:26:07,190 --> 00:26:10,000
you shouldn't be so rude to Brother Hua.

309
00:26:17,460 --> 00:26:19,330
Older Brother.

310
00:26:23,130 --> 00:26:27,930
Since you already called me "Older Brother," then it means you've already forgiven older brother.

311
00:26:30,100 --> 00:26:33,700
Come! Sit here and let this older brother take a good look at you.

312
00:26:46,620 --> 00:26:48,780
To be honest, it is really thoughtless of me.

313
00:26:48,780 --> 00:26:52,480
Xiaolei isn't married yet, she should sit next to her brother.

314
00:26:52,480 --> 00:26:57,110
Xiao Bai, aren't you a fool?

315
00:27:15,540 --> 00:27:18,680
Why are you looking at me?

316
00:27:18,680 --> 00:27:23,380
We all are a family so it doesn't matter where we sit, does it?

317
00:27:25,860 --> 00:27:29,120
Since Xiaolei doesn't want to move,

318
00:27:29,120 --> 00:27:31,100
then I can switch seats with you, Big Brother Hua.

319
00:27:31,100 --> 00:27:33,870
Hero Xiao, please hurry to sit back down.

320
00:27:33,870 --> 00:27:37,460
My little sister has been spoiled too much.

321
00:27:37,460 --> 00:27:40,100
How can you be so impolite in front of our guest?

322
00:27:40,100 --> 00:27:42,030
Do it quickly!

323
00:27:44,970 --> 00:27:46,940
Come and sit over here!

324
00:27:58,040 --> 00:28:00,290
Hero Xiao, please take your seat.

325
00:28:13,380 --> 00:28:15,320
Come, Little Sister.

326
00:28:15,930 --> 00:28:17,650
Eat more!

327
00:28:18,560 --> 00:28:20,600
Just like this!

328
00:28:20,600 --> 00:28:22,680
Have them all!

329
00:28:22,680 --> 00:28:25,500
No problem! Hero Xiao, you should have some, too.

330
00:28:27,390 --> 00:28:30,930
Come on, eat a little.

331
00:28:37,700 --> 00:28:39,700
Have some more.

332
00:28:44,530 --> 00:28:48,370
Brother Hua, please don't bother to see me out. I'll take my leave here.

333
00:28:48,370 --> 00:28:50,590
Little Sister, where are you going?

334
00:28:51,290 --> 00:28:54,400
- Of course, I want to go. 
 - Naturally, she's staying

335
00:28:54,400 --> 00:28:57,490
to reminisce with Brother Hua and Uncle Hua.

336
00:28:57,490 --> 00:28:59,730
It's a relief solution to the pain of the heart.

337
00:28:59,730 --> 00:29:02,500
Hero Xiao, you are still the one who is very considerate.

338
00:29:02,500 --> 00:29:05,160
It's hard to keep a grown-up girl home.

339
00:29:05,160 --> 00:29:10,000
I'm afraid my little sister hasn't totally given in to staying at home yet (lit. not in the heart nor the mind).

340
00:29:12,530 --> 00:29:15,750
Xiaolei and I stayed at the inn because we had no option.

341
00:29:15,750 --> 00:29:18,000
Now that you've reunited,

342
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:21,420
naturally, it would be more appropriate for you to stay at your home.

343
00:29:21,420 --> 00:29:22,810
- No, it's not appropriate.  
 - I shall take my leave.

344
00:29:22,810 --> 00:29:24,600
Goodbye.

345
00:29:24,600 --> 00:29:28,450
No... no... Xiao Bai.

346
00:29:28,450 --> 00:29:30,630
Xiao Bai!

347
00:29:30,630 --> 00:29:32,490
- Stop calling! He's already gone. 
 - Xiao Bai.

348
00:29:32,490 --> 00:29:35,220
It's better to play with me.

349
00:29:35,220 --> 00:29:37,280
Xiao Bai!

350
00:29:38,280 --> 00:29:40,080
Xiao Bai.

351
00:29:40,080 --> 00:29:43,680
[(Left)The flowers bring about the clear morning sun of the sunny Spring day.] - [(Top and Center) The Spring is exuberant] - [(Right) The chirp of the warbler and the hundreds of flowers bring about the sunny Spring day]  

352
00:29:43,680 --> 00:29:46,340
What on earth do you want to do?

353
00:29:46,340 --> 00:29:48,400
I just want to play with you.

354
00:29:48,400 --> 00:29:50,390
You're still acting?

355
00:29:51,060 --> 00:29:54,050
Let me ask you! Where is Hua Que? Where did you hide him?

356
00:29:54,050 --> 00:29:56,120
Why does Master Hua keep saying you're my brother?

357
00:29:56,120 --> 00:29:59,220
It's the truth. I am your brother.

358
00:29:59,220 --> 00:30:01,890
Please! Can you stop lying to me?

359
00:30:01,890 --> 00:30:04,350
- When have I lied to you? 
 - You...

360
00:30:05,620 --> 00:30:08,280
Hua Que came to find me yesterday.

361
00:30:08,280 --> 00:30:10,650
He said that he's my real brother.

362
00:30:11,620 --> 00:30:14,930
Xiao Chun Hua believes the words from a stranger.

363
00:30:14,930 --> 00:30:18,130
Then how do you know that he didn't lie to you?

364
00:30:20,940 --> 00:30:24,110
Fine! Even if he is a liar,

365
00:30:24,110 --> 00:30:25,800
then you aren't a good person, either.

366
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:28,370
What's the point of being a good person?

367
00:30:28,370 --> 00:30:32,160
- It's better to be Xiao Chun Hua's brother. 
 - You see?

368
00:30:32,160 --> 00:30:34,060
Didn't you just admit it?

369
00:30:35,710 --> 00:30:40,110
After I obtain the Xin Fa, you can I can be together forever.

370
00:30:41,510 --> 00:30:43,490
You promised me!

371
00:30:49,970 --> 00:30:52,230
Is this how you lied to Hua Xiaolei?

372
00:30:52,230 --> 00:30:56,150
Let me tell you! I don't remember anything of my past.

373
00:30:56,150 --> 00:30:59,810
I just need to know who I am right now and that's enough.

374
00:31:00,510 --> 00:31:02,980
What Shangguan Chun Hua?

375
00:31:02,980 --> 00:31:05,380
You made all of it up.

376
00:31:05,380 --> 00:31:09,870
I see Shangguan Qiu Yue as my family, but all you want is just to use me.

377
00:31:09,870 --> 00:31:14,020
- I just want to try it and see what the feeling of having a family is. 
 - What feeling?

378
00:31:14,020 --> 00:31:15,850
Happy?

379
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:19,810
When will Chun Hua and Qin Yue come to an end?

380
00:31:19,810 --> 00:31:22,770
- The feeling is quite good. 
 - Good like a f*rt! (a bad swear term)

381
00:31:23,820 --> 00:31:27,760
Then let me ask you! How do you know about my birthmark?

382
00:31:32,460 --> 00:31:34,780
Of course, I know.

383
00:31:37,070 --> 00:31:40,000
You already forgot everything about us.

384
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:42,410
Let alone the birthmark,

385
00:31:42,410 --> 00:31:45,380
every part of your body,

386
00:31:46,010 --> 00:31:48,450
I know it all.

387
00:31:54,870 --> 00:31:58,390
You... you mean...

388
00:31:58,390 --> 00:32:00,750
- You.... 
 - You don't want to marry Xiao Bai. 
 - We...

389
00:32:00,750 --> 00:32:03,990
You said you want to elope with me.

390
00:32:03,990 --> 00:32:07,340
Enough, enough. Stop talking!

391
00:32:09,200 --> 00:32:10,940
Do you recall it now?

392
00:32:10,940 --> 00:32:14,250
I don't remember anything. I won't remember it for the rest of my life.

393
00:32:19,420 --> 00:32:22,180
Actually... actually...

394
00:32:22,180 --> 00:32:25,770
If someone loses their memory, they will change to be someone different.

395
00:32:25,770 --> 00:32:28,420
We can expunge everything that's happened in the past.

396
00:32:28,420 --> 00:32:30,890
Just pretend that it never happened.

397
00:32:32,170 --> 00:32:35,650
I don't care if you believe me or not, but I am not Hua Xiaolei.

398
00:32:37,410 --> 00:32:39,280
I do know.

399
00:32:42,410 --> 00:32:45,050
Hua Xiaolei likes me

400
00:32:45,050 --> 00:32:47,080
