401
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:53,990
That's the general idea.

402
00:32:53,990 --> 00:32:58,760
It's the same as saying Chun Hua has no relationship with Qiu Yue any longer.

403
00:32:58,760 --> 00:33:00,890
How can you say it like that?

404
00:33:00,890 --> 00:33:04,140
Xiao Chun Hua is still my younger sister.

405
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:07,240
Isn't that something you lied?

406
00:33:10,190 --> 00:33:13,290
Xiao Chun Hua want to be with Xiao Bai?

407
00:33:14,040 --> 00:33:16,950
I am originally his fiancée.

408
00:33:20,840 --> 00:33:24,450
The Young Master's fiancée has a close relationship with me.

409
00:33:24,450 --> 00:33:26,900
- The birthmark... 
 - Wait... no...

410
00:33:26,900 --> 00:33:28,920
Not right! Not right! Not right!

411
00:33:28,920 --> 00:33:31,420
Chun Hua is not Hua Xiaolei.

412
00:33:31,420 --> 00:33:34,980
- Because Hua Xiaolei is already dead. 
 - But the birthmark is still there.

413
00:33:34,980 --> 00:33:37,840
Then what do you want to do?

414
00:33:39,540 --> 00:33:44,080
I want to try and see what the feeling of having a family is.

415
00:33:44,750 --> 00:33:46,620
Okay.

416
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:49,990
Older Brother.

417
00:33:50,730 --> 00:33:52,860
Brother Qiu Yue.

418
00:33:53,920 --> 00:33:57,750
You can still continue to be my Qiu Yue brother.

419
00:33:58,520 --> 00:34:01,150
- Is that okay? 
 - Okay.

420
00:34:07,970 --> 00:34:11,710
Then.. can you...

421
00:34:11,710 --> 00:34:14,360
- forget about that matter? 
 - What matter?

422
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:17,530
- It's... 
 - That matter!

